oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Concert for Sponsors at the Bluebird Cafe
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Bluebird Café (Restaurant : Nashville, Tenn.); fund raising; lyricists; Woodcuts (prints);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color window card (blue on white) announcing the Concert for Sponsors with Tom Douglas, Wayland Holyfield, Rivers Rutherford and friends at the Bluebird Cafe on March 29. Event is a songwriters' night to benefit students of the Salama Institute. Poster features a woodcut of a microphone.
